.TH PRODBOX 1
.SH NAME
prodbox \- Home Kubernetes operator
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox
[GLOBAL OPTIONS] COMMAND
.SH DESCRIPTION
Typed command registry for the supported prodbox command surface.
.SH COMMAND GROUPS
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBaws\fR
AWS IAM and quota management
.TP
\fBcharts\fR
Bespoke Helm chart lifecycle
.TP
\fBcluster\fR
Local cluster lifecycle
.TP
\fBcommands\fR
Render the command registry
.TP
\fBconfig\fR
Configuration management
.TP
\fBdev\fR
Developer and CI tooling
.TP
\fBdns\fR
Route 53 inspection
.TP
\fBedge\fR
Public DNS + TLS edge
.TP
\fBgateway\fR
Gateway daemon operations
.TP
\fBhelp\fR
Render help for a command path
.TP
\fBhost\fR
Host prerequisite checks
.TP
\fBnuke\fR
Total teardown of every prodbox-owned AWS resource (operator-only)
.TP
\fBtest\fR
Named test suites
.TP
\fBusers\fR
Operator-invited user management
.TP
\fBvault\fR
Vault secret-management lifecycle
.TP
\fBworkload\fR
Internal public workload runtime
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox config validate\fR
Validate the binary-sibling Dhall config.
.TP
\fBprodbox test all\fR
Run the full test surface.
